To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private DonchianChannel _dch;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_dch = DCH(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_dch.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "upperband", _dch.UpperBand.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "lowerband", _dch.LowerBand.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "donchianchannel", _dch.Current.Value);
}
